# Fix My Builds Discount Restore Behavior

  ## Summary

  The current behavior is split between two sources of truth. My Builds displays the saved build_snapshot, so it can show the discounted total 54,900. But Open/Share rebuilds the PC Builder mostly from the saved
  quote_code, which does not preserve the manual off=10000 discount reliably. The fix is to make saved builds restore from the saved build payload plus a discount lock, not from quote code alone.

