  - Save the changed build; confirm the new saved build does not incorrectly keep the old off=10000.

  ## Assumptions

  - off=10000 is a manual/special discount and should not follow changed builds.
  - Bundle discounts are rule-based and should continue recalculating dynamically.
  - My Builds should prioritize accurate saved-build restoration over the shortest possible URL

