   # Shopify Metaobject Setup: PC Builder Promos

  ## Summary

  Create a new promo metaobject that is separate from the existing cpu_motherboard_bundle metaobject. Keep the current CPU/motherboard bundle system as-is, then add this new promo layer for special
  manual discounts like the 9800X3D full bundle promo.

  ## Create This Metaobject Definition

  In Shopify Admin, go to Settings → Custom data → Metaobjects or Content → Metaobjects, then create:

  Name: PC Builder Promo
  Type: pc_builder_promo
  Storefront access: Enabled

  Fields to add:

  promo_label
  Type: Single line text
  Required: Yes
  Example: 9800X3D Bundle Promo

  is_active
  Type: Boolean
  Required: Yes
  Default: true

  discount_amount
  Type: Integer
  Required: Yes
  Example: 10000

  stack_with_bundle_discount
  Type: Boolean
  Required: Yes
  Default: true

  required_components
  Type: JSON
  Required: Yes

  badge_label
  Type: Single line text
  Required: No
  Example: Limited ₱10,000 Off

  starts_at
  Type: Date and time
  Required: No

  ends_at
  Type: Date and time
  Required: No

  internal_note
  Type: Multi-line text
  Required: No

  ## First Promo Entry Example

  Create one entry:

  Entry name: 9800X3D Bundle Promo
  Handle: 9800x3d-bundle
  promo_label: 9800X3D Bundle Promo
  is_active: true
  discount_amount: 10000
  stack_with_bundle_discount: true
  badge_label: Limited ₱10,000 Off

  For required_components, use this structure:

  [
    {
      "tab": "processor",
      "product_id": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "variant_id": "VARIANT_ID_HERE",
      "label": "Ryzen 7 9800X3D"
    },
    {
      "tab": "motherboard",
      "product_id": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "variant_id": "VARIANT_ID_HERE",
      "label": "B850 Motherboard"
    },
    {
      "tab": "memory",
      "product_id": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "variant_id": "VARIANT_ID_HERE",
      "qty": 1,
      "label": "32GB RAM"
    }
  ]

  ## Behavior This Enables

  If stack_with_bundle_discount is true:

  Raw subtotal - CPU/motherboard bundle discount - promo discount

  Example:

  ₱67,400 - ₱2,500 - ₱10,000 = ₱54,900

  If stack_with_bundle_discount is false:

  Raw subtotal - promo discount

  This lets you override the normal CPU/motherboard bundle discount for promos where you do not want both discounts to apply.

  ## Matching Rules

  The promo applies only if every item in required_components is selected.

  Allowed:

  - Customer adds extra SSD, case, fans, accessories, etc.
  - Promo still applies.

  Not allowed:

  - Customer replaces the required B850 motherboard with B650.
  - Customer removes the required RAM.
  - Customer changes the required CPU.
  - Promo is disabled automatically.

  ## Future URL Shape

  After this metaobject exists, links can become:

  /pages/pc-builder-2?build=ENCODED_BUILD&promo=9800x3d-bundle

  - Do not replace cpu_motherboard_bundle; this new pc_builder_promo sits on top of it.
  - Use required_components JSON because it supports unlimited required items.
  - Shopify supports metaobjects, JSON fields, and storefront access for online store/Liquid usage:
    https://help.shopify.com/en/manual/custom-data/metaobjects
    https://shopify.dev/docs/apps/custom-data/metafields/types


